# handbook

Root host skill for the `handbook` family.

- Installed home: `~/handbook/`
- Installed thin projections: `~/handbook/.agents/skills/handbook/` and `~/handbook/.agents/skills/handbook-charter-intake/`
- Codex discovery glue: `~/.codex/skills/handbook*`
- Compatibility discovery glue: `~/.agents/skills/handbook*`

This root skill is informational and packaging-oriented. Use `handbook-charter-intake` for the charter intake workflow.

Successful user-global installs refresh all three surfaces together:

- `~/handbook/`
- `~/.codex/skills/handbook*`
- `~/.agents/skills/handbook*`

Preferred install/update paths:

- Tagged release install/update: `scripts/handbook/install.sh`
- Source checkout install/update: `cargo install --locked --force --path crates/cli && bash tools/codex/install.sh`

Do not edit generated projections under `.agents/skills/**` by hand. Edit `install/handbook-home/SKILL.md.tmpl`, `install/handbook-home/charter-intake/SKILL.md.tmpl`, or `install/handbook-home/agents/openai.yaml`, then rerun `bash tools/codex/generate.sh`.
